    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是剧集式悬疑冒险游戏《都市传说解体中心》的免费体验版。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个体验版中，您可以游玩完整版第一话《黑暗中窥视的眼睛》的一部分内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/840e3716411fbd96897648dfb36917e1.poster.avif?t=1741073325\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/840e3716411fbd96897648dfb36917e1.webm?t=1741073325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/840e3716411fbd96897648dfb36917e1.mp4?t=1741073325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【通知】2025年1月更新的试玩版可将存档继承至正式版。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※2024年10月发布的试玩版存档数据无法继承，请将试玩版更新至最新版本后重新游玩，重新游玩后的存档可继承到正式版。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解体各种与都市传说相关事件的都市传说解体中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突然出现在女性房间里的神秘男人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个男人究竟是谁，他的目的是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新人调查员福来蓟迎来了她的首次事件调查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当事件的谜团被解体时，揭示出令人惊讶的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/2cc0f621da2e6bb05e8a6f900d3ee619.poster.avif?t=1741073325\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/2cc0f621da2e6bb05e8a6f900d3ee619.webm?t=1741073325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/43029c64945146547c0023860a61cf50.poster.avif?t=1741073325\" width=620 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/43029c64945146547c0023860a61cf50.webm?t=1741073325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/db4efbf81f1bbf96f1fb623abc9014c7.avif?t=1741073325\" width=310 height=310 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >福来蓟：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的主角。她是都市传说解体中心新来的兼职生，在调查过程中被卷入怪异事件。能够通过眼镜看穿人们的想法和残留的意念。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“如果能帮助朋友，我义不容辞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/d24cff9e6e80a283b511a2e3f305a8ba.avif?t=1741073325\" width=310 height=310 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >廻屋涉：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >都市传说解体中心的主任，同时也是国内顶级的灵能者。由于坐轮椅无法进行现场调查，但能够通过灵视看破怪异事件的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“哦，这不是怪异的气息吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269890/extras/c2bbe17ccec429e8a4cb10445a4876c1.avif?t=1741073325\" width=310 height=310 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >茉莉：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真名为止木休美，是都市传说解体中心的现场调查员。看上去像是毫无干劲的兼职员工，但她却是精通驾驶、格斗和间谍活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这次可难得我提得起劲儿！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
